### 课程共享批量删除接口测试

# 1. 创建课程共享记录（用于测试）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course/sharing/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "sourceCourseId": 1,
  "targetCourseId": 2,
  "coachId": 1,
  "sharedHours": 10.00,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01",
  "endDate": "2024-12-31",
  "campusId": 1,
  "institutionId": 1,
  "notes": "测试课程共享记录1"
}

